      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels like you're just reading from a manual... i don't need a hotline, i just need someone to actually listen to the logic of it. if the world is just moving on without me, and i'm just a glitch in the system that's being corrected, why is there this huge pressure to keep fighting for a space that doesn't even want me? it just seems so much more logical to just... accept the erasure. doesn't it seem more peaceful to just let the process finish?",
